article.description: Asante Gist tied his season high with 22 points as Iona got past Siena 73-57 in the Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference tournament semifinals on Sunday night.
article.headline: Gist scores 22 to lift Iona over Siena 73-57 in MAAC tourney
article.linkText: Gist scores 22 to lift Iona over Siena 73-57 in MAAC tourney
article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- Asante Gist tied his season high with 22 points as Iona got past Siena 73-57 in the Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference tournament semifinals on Sunday night. Rickey McGill had 18 points and six rebounds for Iona (16-15). E.J. Crawford added 16 points and eight rebounds. Tajuan Agee had 13 rebounds for the visitors. Evan Fisher had 15 points for the Saints (17-16). Jalen Pickett added 15 points, eight assists and seven rebounds. Kevin Degnan had eight rebounds. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
